productDetail.productDescription: Fast, sleek and powerful - meet the Redmi Go. Its 12.7 cm (5) HD display is designed to deliver sharp and vibrant visuals. Loaded with the Android Oreo (Go edition) OS, the Redmi Go ensures a smooth, light and fast user experience. The Go edition apps that come pre-installed in this smartphone use less RAM and storage, ensuring they load faster than the regular apps. Powered by a Qualcomm Snapdragon 425 processor, this smartphone treats you to a seamless performance. From day to night, now take stunning photos of everyday moments with the 8 MP rear camera (with LED flash) of the Redmi Go. Its 5 MP front camera comes with the AI Beautify technology so that your selfies always look Insta-worthy. To top all this off, the 3000 mAh battery of this smartphone keeps the fun going, almost all day long.

productSpecification.Connectivity technologies: GPRS, EDGE, HSPA+, WCDMA, TD-LTE, 4G LTE, FDD
productSpecification.Special features: Dual SIM, GPS, Music Player, Video Player, Face Unlock, Magnetic induction, Light sensor, Proximity sensor, G-sensor, Acceleration sensor, Other sensors
productSpecification.In The Box: Handset, USB Cable, Sim Tray Ejecter, Pre-applied Screen Protector and Protective Case, Booklet with Warranty Card and Quick Guide
